missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md:75:- **Tran-Yu (2015)** "Depletion of nonlinearity in NS flows" — *Nonlinearity* 28, 1295–1306
missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md:76:- **Tran-Yu (2016)** "Pressure moderation and effective pressure in NS flows" — *Nonlinearity* 29, 2990–3005
missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md:77:- **Tran-Yu (2017)** "Regularity of NS flows with bounds for the pressure" — *Appl. Math. Lett.* 67, 21–27
missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md:78:- **Tran-Yu (2017)** "Note on Prodi-Serrin-Ladyzhenskaya type criteria" — *J. Math. Phys.* 58, 011501
missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md:79:These papers use Prodi-Serrin type criteria (not De Giorgi). Not relevant to the 4/3 question. The "Tran-Yu 2014 AIHPC" reference in the chain must be corrected to Choi-Vasseur 2014.
