missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/mission-context.md:19:- The Lamb vector L = ω × u generates the CZ-lossy pressure piece. For Beltrami flows (L = 0), CZ loss vanishes — but mechanism doesn't survive even 1% perturbation from Beltrami alignment.
